17/  Do not form a #bitcoin opinion based on your historical frames of reference. Bitcoin is different. #famouslastwords
14/ Once the Sw2X drama is behind us  #bitcoin will accelerate even more rapidly..
13/ The #bitcoin train has left the station  and too many stakeholders are already aboard.
8/ Yes  American stocks may draw demand from more than just Americans  but c’mon  #bitcoin is worldwide.
6/ Bitcoin can’t issue shares & dilute like a public company can. I mean  all 21M $BTC haven’t even been mined yet!
5/ ..and that’s not counting the unknown amount lost on USB drives tossed into the garbage before bitcoin was worth anything.
4/ The supply? There are 21M “shares” i.e. 21M bitcoin. That’s it. That’s the supply  for the whole world..
3/ #Bitcoin holders should not really care because either way  they win massively in my opinion.
